---
import PageLayout from '@layouts/PageLayout.astro';
---

<PageLayout title="Mentric — For Organisations" description="Scale coaching across your organisation without losing quality. Programme management, analytics, compliance, and multi-client support for coaching businesses.">

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="relative overflow-hidden bg-glow-gradient">
    <div class="section-container py-10 md:py-14 text-center">
      <p class="category-label mb-4">For Organisations</p>
      <h1 class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        Scale coaching without
        <span class="text-primary">losing quality</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-6 max-w-2xl mx-auto text-lg md:text-xl">
        Manage coaching programmes across teams, track meaningful outcomes at
        every level, and prove return on investment to your stakeholders — all
        from one platform.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-10 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4">
        <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary-lg">Book a Demo</a>
        <a href="/features" class="btn-secondary px-8 py-4 text-base rounded-2xl">
          Explore Features
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Pain Points -->
  <section class="bg-background">
    <div class="section-container py-14 md:py-20">
      <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-14">
        <p class="category-label mb-3">The Problem</p>
        <h2>The challenge of coaching at scale</h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-lg">
          As coaching operations grow, so does the complexity. Without the right
          infrastructure, quality and visibility suffer.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <div class="card-editorial p-6 border-l-2 border-l-primary/30">
          <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink mb-2">No visibility across programmes</h4>
          <p class="text-base text-muted">
            When coaching happens in silos, leadership has no line of sight into
            what's actually working — or what isn't.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="card-editorial p-6 border-l-2 border-l-primary/30">
          <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink mb-2">Inconsistent quality &amp; methodology</h4>
          <p class="text-base text-muted">
            Every coach does things differently. Without shared standards, the
            experience your coachees receive varies wildly.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="card-editorial p-6 border-l-2 border-l-primary/30">
          <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink mb-2">No meaningful outcomes to report</h4>
          <p class="text-base text-muted">
            Stakeholders want proof that coaching delivers results. Anecdotes
            and attendance figures don't cut it.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="card-editorial p-6 border-l-2 border-l-primary/30">
          <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink mb-2">Administrative chaos</h4>
          <p class="text-base text-muted">
            Juggling multiple coaches, coachees, and programmes across
            spreadsheets and email threads is unsustainable.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- How Mentric Helps -->
  <section class="bg-white">
    <div class="section-container py-14 md:py-20">
      <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-10">
        <p class="category-label mb-3">The Solution</p>
        <h2>How Mentric helps</h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-lg">
          Purpose-built for coaching organisations that need structure,
          visibility, and scale — without bureaucracy.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Feature 1: Programme management -->
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center mb-16">
        <div>
          <p class="category-label mb-3">Programmes</p>
          <h3>Programme management, simplified</h3>
          <p class="mt-4">
            Create and manage coaching programmes from a single dashboard.
            Assign coaches with built-in validation, enrol coachees individually
            or in bulk via CSV import, and configure programme-level settings and
            permissions — all without spreadsheets.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-xl">
          <img src="/images/programmes.webp" alt="Programme management dashboard showing coaching programmes, coach assignments, and coachee enrolment" class="w-full rounded-xl shadow-editorial-lg border border-border" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Feature 2: Organisation-wide visibility -->
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center mb-16">
        <div class="order-2 md:order-1 overflow-hidden rounded-xl">
          <img src="/images/analytics.webp" alt="Organisation-wide analytics dashboard with aggregate metrics across all coaching programmes" class="w-full rounded-xl shadow-editorial-lg border border-border" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
        <div class="order-1 md:order-2">
          <p class="category-label mb-3">Analytics</p>
          <h3>Organisation-wide visibility</h3>
          <p class="mt-4">
            See exactly what's happening across every programme, coach, and
            coachee. Track engagement, completion rates, and coaching hours from
            an aggregate dashboard — and use AI-powered queries to surface
            insights across your entire operation.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Feature 3: Standardise without restricting -->
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center mb-16">
        <div>
          <p class="category-label mb-3">Governance</p>
          <h3>Standardise without restricting</h3>
          <p class="mt-4">
            Set organisation-wide coaching rules — goal ownership, journey
            progression, booking permissions — while still allowing
            programme-level overrides where flexibility is needed. Share
            competency frameworks and maintain an assessment template library
            that every coach can draw from.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-xl">
          <img src="/images/command-center.webp" alt="Coach command center showing organisation-wide coaching rules, competency frameworks, and assessment templates" class="w-full rounded-xl shadow-editorial-lg border border-border" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Feature 4: Multi-client support -->
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center mb-16">
        <div class="order-2 md:order-1 overflow-hidden rounded-xl">
          <img src="/images/settings-branding.webp" alt="Client branding settings showing per-client logos, colours, and font configuration for white-labelling" class="w-full rounded-xl shadow-editorial-lg border border-border" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
        <div class="order-1 md:order-2">
          <p class="category-label mb-3">Multi-Client</p>
          <h3>Multi-client support</h3>
          <p class="mt-4">
            For coaching practices managing multiple client organisations,
            Mentric keeps everything separate and branded. Each client gets
            their own logos, colours, and fonts. Configure settings and run
            reports at the client level — or white-label the entire platform
            as your own.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Feature 5: Coach & team management -->
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center mb-16">
        <div>
          <p class="category-label mb-3">Team</p>
          <h3>Coach &amp; team management</h3>
          <p class="mt-4">
            Invite and manage your coaching team with role-based access —
            Admin, Coach, or AdminCoach. Track coach activity, monitor
            caseloads, and keep an eye on messaging and session activity to
            ensure your team is supported and on track.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-xl">
          <img src="/images/coachees.webp" alt="Coach and team management view showing coachee list with role-based access and activity monitoring" class="w-full rounded-xl shadow-editorial-lg border border-border" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Feature 6: Compliance & accreditation -->
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center mb-16">
        <div class="order-2 md:order-1 overflow-hidden rounded-xl">
          <img src="/images/cpd.webp" alt="CPD tracking and compliance dashboard with coaching hours, audit logs, and accreditation evidence" class="w-full rounded-xl shadow-editorial-lg border border-border" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
        <div class="order-1 md:order-2">
          <p class="category-label mb-3">Compliance</p>
          <h3>Compliance &amp; accreditation</h3>
          <p class="mt-4">
            Keep your coaching operation audit-ready. Track CPD across every
            coach, maintain audit logs for compliance, and gather evidence for
            accreditation bodies — all with GDPR-compliant data handling baked
            in from the start.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Feature 7: Enterprise-ready -->
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div>
          <p class="category-label mb-3">Enterprise</p>
          <h3>Enterprise-ready</h3>
          <p class="mt-4">
            Built for organisations that take security, accessibility, and
            performance seriously. Mentric meets WCAG AA/AAA accessibility
            standards, uses secure cookie-based authentication with CSRF
            protection, supports real-time collaboration, and scales
            comfortably to hundreds of coaches and thousands of coachees.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-xl">
          <img src="/images/programmes.webp" alt="Mentric enterprise dashboard demonstrating scalable coaching platform with real-time collaboration" class="w-full rounded-xl shadow-editorial-lg border border-border" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Banner -->
  <section class="bg-plum-gradient">
    <div class="section-container py-14 md:py-20 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-white max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        Ready to bring structure to your coaching operation?
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-primary-200 text-lg max-w-xl mx-auto">
        See how Mentric helps coaching organisations deliver consistent,
        measurable outcomes at scale.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-10">
        <a href="/contact" class="btn-accent px-8 py-4 text-base rounded-2xl">
          Book a Demo
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</PageLayout>
